Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.60,0:22:29.26,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}想要触碰又不愿触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:33.70,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}仅属于我们二人的Swing heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:47.90,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}是从哪裡出现的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:51.26,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}这扇前所未有的门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:52.51,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.70,0:22:56.03,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我还未被人发现的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:59.03,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}因为那一定不是错觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.08,0:23:02.40,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}我也想要确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:07.38,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}即使是我 也想要去抓住那激动人心的一刻
