Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.88,0:23:12.64,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}已经快要溢出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:15.12,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}但是从伸出的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:17.54,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}传来的疑惑的讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:20.22,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}这样的你也很棒哦
