Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:26.48,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}仅属于我们二人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:30.82,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}这样一定能拉近彼此的距离吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:35.52,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}温柔地踩上对方的节拍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:38.17,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}现在也许并不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.70,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}总有一天会心有灵犀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.72,0:23:44.05,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}总有一天会无话不谈
